-- Northern Rock Asset Management to Buy Back Bonds Tendered
-- B y   B e n   M a r t i n
-- 2011-12-15T17:48:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-15/northern-rock-asset-management-to-buy-back-bonds-tendered-1-.html
Northern Rock Asset Management Plc
said it will buy back all the subordinated bonds validly
tendered by investors, according to a statement.  The company is purchasing notes denominated in pounds and
dollars with a face value of about 889 million pounds ($1.4
billion), the statement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
